  ('social-worker-moex-01531', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-108-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '嬰兒被虐待的事件時常在媒體上曝光，關於嬰兒虐待的風險因素，下列何者錯誤？', '["貧窮", "教育程度低", "母親有憂鬱情緒", "兩位以上子女的家庭"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "225c0ce9caca", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7f33815a6b91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "107", "s": "0605", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-01532', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-108-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '同儕關係在幼兒發展過程中扮演重要角色，下列何者錯誤？', '["同儕所提供的學習環境與家庭近似", "同儕之間的關係較為平等", "同儕提供兒童社交學習的機會", "同儕提供與他人相比較的機會有助瞭解自我"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:09+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "225c0ce9caca", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7f33815a6b91", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108020", "c": "107", "s": "0605", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
